                        <img src="/assets/images/ChatGPT Image Dec 29, 2025, 09_50_40 PM (1).png" alt="Matt training with a Dachshund on the beach" class="owner-image">
                        <img src="/assets/images/IMG_4770 (1).PNG" alt="Matt playing with a black Labrador" class="owner-image">
                    </div>
